    <string name="welcome_p1">Welcome %s to NoExcuse 💪\n\nWe are delighted to welcome you.\nChoosing this app is a strong step—it shows that you care about your time, your goals, and the person you want to become.\nThis space is yours.</string>
    <string name="welcome_p2">Awaken the beast within you. 🔥\nSuccess waits for no one. Every second lost is a missed opportunity. Today, you have a choice: remain the same… or become extraordinary.\nNoExcuse is more than just an app: it’s the spark that ignites your inner fire, the force that drives you when you want to give up, and the energy that turns your dreams into reality.\nBreak your limits. Dominate your fears. Outdo yourself every single day.\nNo excuses. No turning back. Only victory.</string>
    <string name="welcome_p3">NoExcuse brings together everything you need to progress. 🔥\nPlan your tasks, organize your days, track your workouts, improve your sleep, and structure your study sessions in one app.\nThanks to smart reminders, performance tracking, and interactive avatars, NoExcuse helps you stay focused, consistent, and productive every day.\nAn app designed to turn your goals into results. </string>
